data.description:
This home has it all! If you are downsizing, relocating, or looking for a seasonal spot to call your own, you don't want to miss this. Thoughtfully updated in 2022, this two-bedroom, one-bathroom condo is a stunner. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, quartz countertops with waterfall island, new appliances, new insulation, pull-out drawers in kitchen, neutral color palate, and NO POPCORN!
 
Situated on a corner lot, this condo offers more than just a beautiful interior. Enjoy the benefits of a well-maintained neighborhood, filled with amenities and opportunities for an active lifestyle. Whether you're strolling through the streets or taking advantage of the nearby recreational facilities, you'll find that this condo provides the ideal base for embracing the Sun City way of life.
